<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background-color: #0066cc; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 30px 20px; background-color: #f9f9f9; }
    .footer { padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #0066cc; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to MediConnect</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <%= @user_name %>,</p>

      <p><%= @notification.message %></p>

      <p>MediConnect makes it easy to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Book appointments with qualified doctors</li>
        <li>Manage your medical records</li>
        <li>Get timely reminders for your appointments</li>
        <li>Communicate securely with healthcare providers</li>
      </ul>

      <p>We're here to help you on your healthcare journey.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>The MediConnect Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2024 MediConnect. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
